年轻人大些，但体重从175斤不知不觉的降到了152斤，啤酒肚没有了，胸肌腹肌也成型了。"},"attached_info":"CkAImMLilLrczMJLEAMaCTExMDYwNDQ5MyDegam3BjAAOMoBQBxyCTY2NzQ3MDM5MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"7 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c9d66eda72e5da39a7de009f0a7404c8_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1728451196.126016","card_id":"Q_784002372","target":{"id":784002372,"title":"2024 乒乓球亚锦赛女团八强赛首局，孙颖莎 1:3 意外不敌朝鲜金琴英，如何评价这场比赛？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/784002372","type":"question","created":1728397491,"answer_count":328,"follower_count":466,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[14677,181127,407195,2005723,2956962],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"2024乒乓球亚锦赛女团1/4决赛 中国 vs 朝鲜： 第一场：孙颖莎 1:3 金琴英 第二场：王艺迪vs边松景 第三场：石洵瑶vs车秀英 第四场：孙颖莎vs边松景 第五场：王艺迪vs金琴英"},"attached_info":"CkAImMLilLrczMJLEAMaCTExMTAxOTMzMyCzgZW4BjAAONIDQB1yCTc4NDAwMjM3MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"7 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-0f4b012fb4a5fd46dec160a00b91168e_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}]}],"description":{"time":"2024-10-09 13:19:56"}}